Class BaseFileSystem<P extends BasePath<P>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.FileSystem
      • com.palantir.giraffe.file.base.BaseFileSystem<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of path used by the file system
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public abstract class BaseFileSystem<P extends BasePath<P>>
extends FileSystem
    An abstract FileSystem implementation that provides common functionality and additional structure for subclasses.
